text: The Pixel 9, Pixel 9 Pro and Pixel 9 Pro XL are Android smartphones from the Google Pixel product line. They next to the Pixel 8. The phones were announced on August 13, 2024 and were started in United States on August 22, 2024. ==Related pages== * Pixel 9 Pro Fold ==References== ==Other websites== * Pixel 9 Category:Google mobile phones Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2024 Category:Android smartphones
